 type-page status-publish hentry\">\n        <div class=\"entry-body\">\n    <h2>お電話・FAXでのお問い合わせ</h2>\n<p><strong>TEL：092-865-0808　FAX：092-865-1777</strong><br />\n受付時間：平日10:00～18:00（土日祝日休み）</p>\n<p>※こちらのお電話からはタクシーのご予約を承ることができません。<br />\n　タクシーのご予約は<a href=\"tel:0570081234\">「0570-08-1234」</a>福岡交通配車センターまでお願いいたします。</p>\n<hr>\n<span class=\"text-danger\">*</span>は必須入力項目となります。<br />\n<div role=\"form\" class=\"wpcf7\" id=\"wpcf7-f97-p91-o1\" lang=\"ja\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div class=\"screen-reader-response\"></div>\n<form action=\"/inquiry/#wpcf7-f97-p91-o1\" method=\"post\" class=\"wpcf7-form\" novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n<div style=\"display: none;\">\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7\" value=\"97\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_version\" value=\"5.0.3\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_locale\" value=\"ja\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_unit_tag\" value=\"wpcf7-f97-p91-o1\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_container_post\" value=\"91\" />\n</div>\n<p><label> お問い合わせ項目<span class=\"text-danger\">*</span><br />\n    <span class=\"wpcf7-form-control-wrap your-subject\"><select name=\"your-subject\" class=\"wpcf7-form-control wpcf7-select wpcf7-validates-as-required\" aria-required=\"true\" aria-invalid=\"false\"><option value=\"\">---</option><option value=\"サービスについて\">サービスについて</option><option value=\"送迎について\">送迎について</option><option value=\"観光タクシーについて\">観光タクシーについて</option><option value=\"その他お問い合わせ\">その他お問い合わせ</option></select></span></label></p>\n<p><label> お問い合わせ内容<span class=\"text-danger\">*</span><br />\n    <span class=\"wpcf7-form-control-wrap your-message\"><textarea name=\"your-message\" cols=\"40\" rows=\"10\" class=\"wpcf7-form-control wpcf7-textarea wpcf7-validates-as-required\" aria-required=\"true\" aria-invalid=\"false\"></textarea></span> </label></p>\n<p><label> 氏名<span class=\"text-danger\">*</span><br />\n    <span class=\"wpcf7-form-control-wrap your-name\"><input type=\"text\" name=\"your-name\" value=\"\" size=\"40\" class=\"wpcf7-form-control wpcf7-text wpcf7-validates-as-required\" aria-required=\"true\" aria-invalid=\"false\" /></span> </label></p>\n<p><label> フリガナ<span class=\"text-danger\">*</span><br />\n    <span class=\"wpcf7-form-control-wrap your-furikana\"><input type=\"text\" name=\"your-furikana\" value=\"\" size=\"40\" class=\"wpcf7-form-control wpcf7-text wpcf7-validates-as-required\" aria-required=\"true\" aria-invalid=\"false\" /></span> </label></p>\n<p><label> 電話番号<span class=\"text-danger\">*</span><br />\n    <span class=\"wpcf7-form-control-wrap your-tel\"><input type=\"tel\" name=\"your-tel\" value=\"\" size=\"40\" class=\"wpcf7-form-control wpcf7-text wpcf7-tel wpcf7-validates-as-required wpcf7-validates-as-tel\" aria-required=\"true\" aria-invalid=\"false\" /></span> </label></p>\n<p><label> メールアドレス<span class=\"text-danger\">*</span><br />\n    <span class=\"wpcf7-form-control-wrap your-email\"><input type=\"email\" name=\"your-email\" value=\"\" size=\"40\" class=\"wpcf7-form-control wpcf7-text wpcf7-email wpcf7-validates-as-required wpcf7-validates-as-email\" aria-required=\"true\" aria-invalid=\"false\" /></span> </label></p>\n<p><input type=\"submit\" value=\"送信\" class=\"wpcf7-form-control wpcf7-submit\" /></p>\n<div class=\"wpcf7-response-output wpcf7-display-none\"></div></form></div></p>\n    </div>\n\t    </div><!-- [ /#post-91 ] -->\n\n\t\n</div><!-- [ /.mainSection ] -->\n\n</div><!-- [ /.row ] -->\n</div><!-- [ /.container ] -->\n</div><!-- [ /.siteContent ] -->\n<div class=\"section sectionBox siteContent_after\">\n    <div class=\"container \">\n        <div class=\"row \">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 \">\n            <aside class=\"widget widget_vkexunit_banner\" id=\"vkexunit_banner-2\"><a href=\"/bosyuu/\" ><img src=\"https://bunka-taxi.co.jp/wp/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/4f141f6e575cf0685ca004dda71e7550.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></aside><aside class=\"widget widget_vkexunit_contact_section\" id=\"vkexunit_contact_section-3\"><d